# Background Videos

This folder contains background video files for hero sections, page backgrounds, and ambient video effects.

Recommended specifications:
- Format: MP4 (H.264 codec)
- Resolution: 1920x1080 or higher
- Duration: 10-30 seconds (loopable)
- File size: Keep under 10MB for web performance

Usage:
```typescript
import heroBackground from '@/assets/videos/background/hero-bg.mp4';

// Use in video element
<video autoPlay muted loop className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover">
  <source src={heroBackground} type="video/mp4" />
</video>
```

Tips:
- Use short, loopable clips for seamless backgrounds
- Optimize video files for web (compress for smaller file sizes)
- Consider providing multiple formats (MP4, WebM) for browser compatibility